name: Crying Eyes Token
description:
The crying eyes are entities that guard souls in their life journey. They roam between dimensions but, they can't experience life in any of them unless they choose a soul to observe, influence, and become their dimensional guardian. Thus, developing a lifelong connection with their guarded soul.

This piece was created in collaboration with @truenoir_.
Based on his unique Cring Eyes collection.
